title: Taco Bus - Food Truck
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Mexican, Take-out only, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Taco trucks operating at multiple Florida cities. Offers a variety of fillings including tofu, vegan cheese, tempeh, butternut squash and steak strips. Vegan items are cooked on the same grill as meat. Rice, beans, guacamole and salsa are vegan.
